  "detailed_description": "Add to your wish list!!<br><br>A great power war is going on, fight for victory!!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825690/extras/ea6cd569596ac4a468512cb26284e81d.poster.avif?t=1730510218\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825690/extras/ea6cd569596ac4a468512cb26284e81d.webm?t=1730510218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Game features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play in 3 different game modes, an Infinite Mode to challenge your abilities, an Adventure Mode with 35 levels to challenge your skills and a Survival Mode to challenge your stamina.<br></li><li> Defeat several different bosses and enemies.<br></li><li> Extremely accurate controls.<br></li><li> Use over 80 different shots to defeat your enemies.<br></li><li> Buy powerful ships, special shots and mini ships to help you in battle and get a high score. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825690/extras/50a292370ed6b72dd7a2e223f7df7f28.poster.avif?t=1730510218\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825690/extras/50a292370ed6b72dd7a2e223f7df7f28.webm?t=1730510218\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825690/extras/50a292370ed6b72dd7a2e223f7df7f28.mp4?t=1730510218\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong> - Move in all four directions to dodge enemies and enemy shots, destroy all bosses, enemies and everything you see ahead, collect crystals to spend in the store, grab upgrades to strengthen your shots and mini ships to help you in battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1825690/extras/3bd35ec58512ed33ebb85e3c7fdb83d4.avif?t=1730510218\" width=682 height=270 /></span>",
